{"tid":876130,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"死啦,我發春夢遇上愛","createTime":"2018-10-25T11:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T18:52:50.000Z","uid":140357,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1541b0ce16c44d569b21d097b68979e352a463a6","tid":876130,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T11:48:34.000Z","msg":"最近,d A0絲打係咁喺A0 post話自己發春夢,好開心。搞到我潛移默化,今朝都發埋一份(利申:近排好耐冇發過).講下個夢先,除左有d發夢時正常的bug情節,大概係有我,女神同一個男配角。女神個樣似黑木美紗,外表冷冰冰,但其實口硬心軟。故事開始當然係我同個男配角爭女神,而女神又同我係死對頭(偽戀果隻)。但經過一系列事件(包括我個人魅力),女神認清自己不喜歡男配而係喜歡我。雖然對我愛理不理,但心裡因為我言行而甜絲絲。最後差唔多有甜故時,竟然.....竟然....我醒左。。。。。wtf<br />\n<br />\n依家我發覺對女神念念不忘,動左真情添。。。。<br />\n<br />\n希望今晚可以再見到女神佢。。。。。"},{"pid":"3cec507de26f1421273f2076b9a26dacaab2805c","tid":876130,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"個夢d感情好真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4456137cdccb94cb1e4b8deefb1c9c990aa9ec","tid":876130,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T21:35:57.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲試過?"},{"pid":"9cc4ab6cac7df948b09169712a433dfa73983cfd","tid":876130,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T21:36:54.000Z","msg":"好耐冇發過"},{"pid":"5d404fad8650328bba61e9a1c789fd9840408f7c","tid":876130,"uid":214581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"夢始終都係夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5cce7305306d6c09ea02949f3644cecf561dfea","tid":876130,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d404fad8650328bba61e9a1c789fd9840408f7c","tid":876130,"uid":214581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"夢始終都係夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/d